casebody.data:
SOLIS INTERNATIONAL INVESTMENTS, LLC, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
WILMINGTON TRUST, N.A., etc., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D16-1053 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. DECEMBER 14, 2017 FERNANDEZ, LOGUE and SCALES, JJ., concur.

ORDERED that appellant's notice of voluntary dismissal of appeal is recognized by the Court, and this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is hereby dismissed.
